cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper introduces a novel method for image representation in computer vision tasks. 
2. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also likely as the paper proposes a representation of images that is entirely expressed with natural language. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper discusses the efficiency of numerical representations in the proposed method. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a likely category as the paper addresses the question of computation intelligibility in computer vision tasks. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also possible as the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed method on semantic content-based image retrieval.
